{"tid":935224,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［舊書送贈/以書易書］愛書之人有福了","createTime":"2018-12-10T00:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T13:03:24.000Z","uid":114539,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ad17b7e5ad6bba5feffd6bba2f10f777e42599","tid":935224,"uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T00:34:33.000Z","msg":"話說近日執房 清咗少少唔再睇嘅書出嚟<br />\n所以放上嚟睇下搵唔搵到有緣人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔介意大家交換書睇下 隨心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大部分都仲好新 有啲就好殘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點都好 有啲書我keep咗好多年 陪住我成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望搵到有心人接收佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講咁多 大家睇相啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n血腥懸疑類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHEnfbF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHEnfbF.png&h=2f50e249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛情小說類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Ap6GSE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Ap6GSE.png&h=4813920f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yg4uEEk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYg4uEEk.png&h=2bb39196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ： <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7kd6jL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7kd6jL.png&h=679c0158&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9xj1S5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9xj1S5.png&h=86b53a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCU6GTS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCU6GTS.png&h=b00dd1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J7Vqc0x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ7Vqc0x.png&h=4619fd80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢本私心推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mDftVer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmDftVer.png&h=ab2ff419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地作家類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQEVAeE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQEVAeE.png&h=5774e17b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XGwS1k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XGwS1k.png&h=0b20af16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（其實我仲啲本地作家嘅書想轉贈 不過未清完書櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n唔知點分類類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7QeVAfj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7QeVAfj.png&h=0df498fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZNsrm0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZNsrm0.png&h=f51b7fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩本幾好睇 我睇咗幾次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uS6Qo9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuS6Qo9d.png&h=46542c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超級殘舊類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jb2j1Wa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjb2j1Wa.png&h=df4c85da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tE37rnR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtE37rnR.png&h=68bae363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最左嗰本我唔係借完書唔還 係中學嗰陣圖書館館長送俾我嘅 我都睇咗呢本幾次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過殘到咁應該冇人想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有啲神學類、唐詩三百首（個包裝超靚）、論語、孫子兵法、古文觀止等等都想轉贈<br />\n睇下大家對呢啲有冇興趣先再睇下放唔放上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全部書免費 唯一心願係幫佢地搵到惜書之人 <br />\n搵到同好 可以嘅話都想同大家交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次放住少少先 下次再睇下有冇書想放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎tg我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/bolormuddo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbolormuddo&d=mOOqusq6CDDkUJq3KbKzOJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=acc52291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/bolormuddo</a>"},{"pid":"e892f91fc2e4a6675a6cb5c1dd955105ca96da87","tid":935224,"uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T00:38:52.000Z","msg":"自push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605bb7122ee7ce00eee08faf19b1c99f790542d5","tid":935224,"uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T00:46:51.000Z","msg":"Just a girl standing in front of a boy <br />\n同 <br />\n型男講座已經有人接收喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9a5ff545fa36daff074e249b1a9776d73ae823","tid":935224,"uid":27591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T00:46:51.000Z","msg":"幫推.近年都係睇電子書多"},{"pid":"7c0d78af3ebaf1fda29e45d5aa777732e5a3bc87","tid":935224,"uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c9a5ff545fa36daff074e249b1a9776d73ae823","tid":935224,"uid":27591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T00:46:51.000Z","msg":"幫推.近年都係睇電子書多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T00:47:47.000Z","msg":"我都有半年左右冇睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電子書好方便 但係始終鐘意實體書嘅質感同氣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b397b8f97dd4dc7e4bac212fa754fbc957b94b1d","tid":935224,"uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T00:55:02.000Z","msg":"仲有仲有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tc3Ldes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftc3Ldes.png&h=3b1baf46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fh6Qpk8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFh6Qpk8.png&h=f9db4a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KskxCF9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKskxCF9.png&h=7e3a9558&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFtOVsQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFtOVsQ.png&h=3a426b88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUhv8NR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUhv8NR.png&h=edb6796a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zN4tNR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zN4tNR.png&h=1218482c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8AQ8NS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8AQ8NS.png&h=d90c74c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFXPEUy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFXPEUy.png&h=b913932a&s=